{"id":48,"name_zh":"公眾地方擾亂秩序","name_en":"","content_zh":"公眾地方內擾亂秩序行為：\n\n(1) 任何人在為某事情而召開的公眾聚集中作出擾亂秩序行為，或煽惑他人作出此種行為，以阻止處理該事情，即屬犯罪\n\n(2) 任何人在公眾地方作出喧嘩或擾亂秩序的行為，或使用恐嚇性、辱罵性或侮辱性的言詞，或派發或展示任何載有此等言詞的文稿，意圖激使他人破壞社會安寧，或其上述行為相當可能會導致社會安寧破壞，即屬犯罪","content_en":"","defendants":[{"person":{"id":"73e6ba86-df37-4798-ae66-0526429646b7","initial_zh":"譚","initial_en":"","hide_name":false,"gender":"male","image_url":"https://www.hkprotestdb.com/upload/images/2021-04-21/6e28df11-5bbc-4227-a59e-2fbe4818d434/raw.jpg","case_person":[{"arrest_age":null,"occupation":{"type_zh":"人民力量副主席","type_en":""},"status":{"id":2,"type_zh":"還柙","type_en":"還柙"}},{"arrest_age":null,"occupation":{"type_zh":"人民力量副主席","type_en":""},"status":{"id":2,"type_zh":"還柙","type_en":"還柙"}},{"arrest_age":null,"occupation":{"type_zh":"人民力量副主席","type_en":""},"status":{"id":2,"type_zh":"還柙","type_en":"還柙"}},{"arrest_age":null,"occupation":{"type_zh":"人民力量副主席","type_en":""},"status":{"id":2,"type_zh":"還柙","type_en":"還柙"}},{"arrest_age":null,"occupation":null,"status":{"id":2,"type_zh":"還柙","type_en":"還柙"}}]},"case":{"type":"original","progress":{"id":4,"type_zh":"審訊","type_en":"審訊"}},"progress":{"id":1,"type_zh":"審訊","type_en":"審訊","fill":"#0c2c96","contrast":"#FFFFFF","i18nText":"case.in_progress"},"id":"73e6ba86-df37-4798-ae66-0526429646b7"},{"person":{"id":"50fc4632-f2b3-41d6-a91d-2e90776d5d19","initial_zh":"杜","initial_en":"","hide_name":true,"gender":"male","image_url":null,"case_person":[{"arrest_age":null,"occupation":{"type_zh":"學生","type_en":"學生"},"status":{"id":3,"type_zh":"服刑中","type_en":"服刑中"}},{"arrest_age":null,"occupation":{"type_zh":"學生","type_en":"學生"},"status":{"id":3,"type_zh":"服刑中","type_en":"服刑中"}}]},"case":{"type":"original","progress":{"id":8,"type_zh":"結案","type_en":"結案"}},"progress":{"id":2,"type_zh":"結案","type_en":"結案","fill":"#94bbea","contrast":"#FFFFFF","i18nText":"case.closed"},"id":"50fc4632-f2b3-41d6-a91d-2e90776d5d19"},{"person":{"id":"19bf36f1-1073-46bf-bdd9-2bed9768ec2f","initial_zh":"凌","init